Resource Profile: ServiceRequest LE

Official URL: https://interoperabilidad.minsal.cl/fhir/ig/tei/StructureDefinition/ServiceRequestLE Version: 0.2.2
Standards status: Draft Maturity Level: 0 Computable Name: ServiceRequestLE

ServiceRequest LE recurso utilizado para la representación de los datos de la interconsulta.

Usages:

  • Use this Profile: Bundle Agendar LE, Bundle Atender LE, Bundle Iniciar LE, Bundle Priorizar LE... Show 3 more, Bundle Referenciar LE, Bundle Revisar LE and Bundle Terminar LE
  • Refer to this Profile: Encounter Atender LE, MessageHeader LE and Solicitud de Examen LE
  • Examples for this Profile: ServiceRequest/EjemploSolicitudInterconsultaFinalizada

You can also check for usages in the FHIR IG Statistics
